1.title: Assets
1.definition: International investment position, reserve assets (position at end of quarter vis-à-vis non-residents; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

1452173895267.title: Assets ratio
1452173895267.definition: International investment position, reserve assets as percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (position at end of quarter vis-à-vis non-residents; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 and ESA 2010 standards).
